{
  "text": "It is important that an athlete learn how to cope with destructive self-statements that negatively influence an appraisal, coping and affective reactions, and finally sport motivation [CITATION_1] . There are some strategies that can help athletes in coping, e.g., self-statement modification, imagery, Socratic dialog, corrective experiences, modeling, self-analysis, storytelling, metaphors and reframing [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "143247059",
